						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d1283e132" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                DOLâ€™s administration and enforcement authoritiesunder the statutes and under the Executive orders implementedin this part do not limit the authority of contractingofficers to administer and enforce the terms and conditions ofagency contracts. However, DOL has regulatory authority torequire contracting agencies to change contract terms toinclude missing contract clauses or wage determinations thatare required by the FAR, or to withhold contract amounts (see,e.g., 22.1015, 22.1022).</p>
